{"tid":1791706,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭民望 56％人畀零分","createTime":"2019-12-21T05:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T05:31:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a843bd1aa51dd026ae1ae58ae3eeaef68416c5dd","tid":1791706,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T05:14:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191221/BZNZHYUDBG37RGSUUOUMYEDCKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191221%2FBZNZHYUDBG37RGSUUOUMYEDCKY%2F&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQUv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=27b6a1ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191221%2FBZNZHYUDBG37RGSUUOUMYEDCKY%2F&h=c1a724f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191221/BZNZHYUDBG37RGSUUOUMYEDCKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭民望 56％人畀零分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191221/large/1576858872_4383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576858872_4383.jpg&h=02d1a53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最新的民調顯示，有56％受訪者給林鄭0分。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥堅拒回應民間五大訴求，民望續在低位徘徊。最新的民調顯示，市民對林鄭的評分只有19.6分，較上次稍跌，在約1,000受訪者當中，<span style=\"color: orange;\">56％人給予林鄭月娥零分，反對她出任特首的比率更連續四次逾八成。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">68％人不滿警獲OT錢</span><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：踢保教師轟警濫捕致準則不公<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所本月13至18日，即監警會的國際專家小組集體「跳船」後，成功訪問了逾千名市民。結果顯示，受訪者給予林鄭的評分，與兩周前的調查時微跌0.1分。支持林鄭出任特首的比率增加了兩個百分點至12％，反對她出任特首的比率減少了兩個百分點至81％，兩者相減的支持率淨值則為負68百分點。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所公佈另一個「我們香港人」的調查結果，調查於本月16日至17日進行，約有1,000受訪者，題目是詢問市民對有1.1萬位警員在過半年獲發放共9.5億元的超時津貼、每人平均獲8.6萬元的滿意程度，68％對此感到不滿，24％人對此感到滿意，滿意率淨值是負44個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然、何嘉瑤"},{"pid":"49c3d036758ac43c161f56a7eada6c90b8a853dd","tid":1791706,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">杜絕政治酬庸<br />\n銀髮族集會</span><br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間:下午1時至5時<br />\n地點:愛丁堡廣場大會堂對出空地<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對通知書</span><br />\nfacebook銀髮族老而不廢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">毋忘721恐襲<br />\nRemembering 721 Terror</span><br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間 : 15:00<br />\n地點: <br />\n- 元朗 YOНО MALL<br />\n- 尖沙咀 海港城"},{"pid":"a8a37d151bf6b3d7476cf7da3d2c1d2964fb0dc7","tid":1791706,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"仲有44%有分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n半杯水的哲學"},{"pid":"2246700bb8f81f02b59e6c17abd5e48f2642a3f6","tid":1791706,"uid":310342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"0分都俾多咗，支持下年負分制"}]}